        <li><a href="#medical-asepsis" style="color:#4f46e5; text-decoration:none;">Medical Asepsis (Clean Technique)</a></li>
        <li><a href="#surgical-asepsis" style="color:#4f46e5; text-decoration:none;">Surgical Asepsis (Sterile Technique)</a></li>
